Colour in life.
Ground colour transparent. Carapace and abdomen with fine longitudinal black stripes made up of black dots in females (fig 
1
C). Males sparsely dotted with black dots (fig 
1
D), without distinct stripes. The colour patterns still remain in some specimens kept in alcohol with white dots, longitudinally striated. [Based on specimens: NSMT-Cr 
1918
; 
1919
; 
1920
; 
1921
; 
1933
; 
1955
; 
1961
